- Speaker B tells the group that he was in an institution and began talking very badly and everything. He thinks it might be the effect of the drugs or the combination of the two.
- Speaker B wants to bat his head against the wall because he likes seeing others get worse. But the hospital staff doesn't allow him to do so, so he decides to work from the laundry.
